text:
Kogatan and Mamimin, you guys don't think
about clothes and fashion, huh, Producer?

Well, yeah.
Both of them have good taste in their own way.

Huh...?
D-don't expect any compliments from me~?

Well, I'll graciously accept that--
... So, Producer, what kind of style do you like?

I've been seeing it a lot lately, you know.
It looks really stylish.

I know, right!
It makes your figure look good, and the silhouette is cute!

Huh...
Are you, by any chance, talking about yourself?

It's surprisingly unexpected, but...
I wonder, does it suit me...?
I mean, I do try to keep up with the trends.

Hmm...
As expected of the talented Producer!
